							</span>
			<a href="http://werblog.com/2005/09/the-great-internet-transformation-a-first-stab/#comment-56" class="social-posted-when" target="_blank">September 21, 2005</a>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="social-comment-body">
				<p>It seems that Google is trying to open access to all whereas Yahoo and others are trying to capture prime content and thus develop the fiefdom.  With the suit by the author&#8217;s guild going forward, it seems that some would rather fight than accept a bonus check. I like your &#8220;combos&#8221;.  It is intriguing to speculate on who will marry whom.  Will Google need a cellular  partner or will it count on open cellular browsers?</p>
